item.description: So cool to read about your trip and see the photos. The people of Jordon sound the most interesting. The map was super helpful as we track your travel. We hope you are feeling better. Looking forward to more postings and impressions. Lots of Love, E, S, J, and E (and W)
item.content:encoded:
So cool to read about your trip and see the photos. The people of Jordon sound the most interesting. The map was super helpful as we track your travel. We hope you are feeling better. Looking forward to more postings and impressions.
